
config VIDEO_FACETIMEHD
    tristate "Apple FaceTime HD (Broadcom 1570) camera support"
    depends on PCI && VIDEO_DEV && MEDIA_PCI_SUPPORT
    select VIDEOBUF2_DMA_SG
    select V4L2_FWNODE
    help
      This driver adds support for the Broadcom BCM15700A0 PCIe camera found
      in newer Apple MacBook laptops. You must install firmware manually in:

        /lib/firmware/facetimehd/firmware.bin

      Without the firmware, the camera will not function.
